---
title: Beef Sub and Truffled Bacon Mushroom Sauce with chips and cabbage slaw
description: This loaded sub is positively chock-a-block with amazing ingredients. Rich tomato-y beef mince, salty bacon bits, and a truffled mushroom sauce all add to the excitement. Classic sides of crispy chips and creamy coleslaw make for an altogether enticing meal.
